shuttle pharmaceuticals inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Biotech & Pharma
Sub-Industry: Specialty Pharma
Shuttle Pharmaceuticals, Inc. produces and distributes pharmaceutical products. The Company develops drugs to sensitize cancers to radiation therapy and to protect normal tissues from radiation injury. Shuttle Pharmaceuticals markets its products worldwide.




